      <title>报告称中国民兵在南海的存在有所增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/china-militia-presence-increases-in-south-china-sea-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于华盛顿的亚洲海事透明倡议组织的数据显示，去年，随着北京在地区紧张局势加剧的情况下继续加强其存在，中国在南海主要岛礁周围的海上民兵船只数量增加了35%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/china-militia-presence-increases-in-south-china-sea-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
