      <title>美国立法者达成协议以避免政府即将关门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/lawmakers-reach-deal-to-avert-us-government-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会领导人在最后一刻达成了一项协议，以避免美国政府造成破坏性关门，这引发了与迅速抨击该协议的极端保守派的另一场冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/lawmakers-reach-deal-to-avert-us-government-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
